{
  "text": "where the wavevector magnitude is given by k 2\u03c0\u2215\u03bb, \u03bb is the wavelength of the incident plane wave associated with the ray, and L is the etalon thickness. Under conditions when \u03b8 \u03bb \u226a 1, Eq. (1) can be expanded to second order in \u03b8 \u03bb to obtain an approximate dispersion relation [CITATION_1] ",
